Tornom: Evasive Bittorrent In The Cloud

1) edit bootstrap script to include your email address
2) create EC2 instance with bootstrap_chef.sh as user_data
3) download stuff on port 80
4) terminate instance and get email report of your EC2 bill

Work in progress. This is a chef cookbook for a torrent download/seed/download system in the cloud. The intended deploy
target is Amazon EC2.

Ubuntu Lucid AMI: ami-6407f20d
